- use runfile	
- verify: http://xcat-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/advanced/gpu/nvidia/verify_cuda_install.html

cudnn: 
- http://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/sdk/cudnn-install/index.html#installlinux-tar

